title: The Last Episode of Season One
description:
A new moon cycle means new manifestations! Join Camo as they share their hopes for the future and reflect on the first season of Unfazed and Unbothered. Camo dishes about the drama that unfolded on his most recent trip to Six Flags, recounts paranormal activity and hints at the exciting new moments to come in Season Two of Unfazed and Unbothered.
